title: latest update of Firefox
content: Since the latest Firefox update, a little notification icon about autofill addresses has appeared to the left of the web address line. It keeps asking if I want to save an address that I entered in someone's contact, so no I never want to save that in my autofill, but it doesn't give me that option. Has this happened to anyone else?
creator: livingsed

title: Firefox keeps crashing
content: Firefox keeps crashing. Refreshed; no change. Uninstalled and reinstalled; no change. Crashes right upon startup.
creator: mbgwenatchee

title: Firefox keeps asking me if I want to save an address that I entered in a contact and I can't get it to stop.
content: Firefox keeps asking me if I want to save an address that I entered in a contact and I can't get it to stop. It doesn't have NEVER as a choice. I tried saving it and it went in my autofill, but I don't want it there. I deleted it and then it started asking me if I want to save it again. HELP!
creator: livingsed

title: some popup windows and post-order features of Instacart don't work in firefox, but do in Chrome
content: I have had trouble with Instacart features such as adding items to a pending order, or leaving feedback or a tip for a shopper. Most of the same Instacart features seem to work correctly in Chrome, but of course I would rather use Firefox. But having said that, some don't work properly in Chrome either!
creator: dana30
